biography_text: GOSAR, Paul, a Representative from Arizona; born in Rock Springs, Sweetwater County, Wyo., November 22, 1958; graduated from Pinedale High School, Pinedale, Wyo., 1977; B.S., Creighton University, Omaha, Nebr., 1981; D.D.S., Creighton University, Omaha, Nebr., 1985; dentist; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Twelfth and to the three succeeding Congresses (January 3, 2011-present).
